            <div class="help-section" id="faqs">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> 7. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h2>
                <p>Here are answers to common questions:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>How do I reset my password?</strong>
                        <p class="faq-answer answer-yes">Contact Technical Support to reset and provide new login credentials.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Why can’t I submit a checklist?</strong>
                        <p class="faq-answer answer-no">Ensure all required fields (name, date, shift type, checklist) are completed. If the issue persists, contact Technical Support.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>What if I see an error message?</strong>
                        <p class="faq-answer answer-no">Note the message and contact Technical Support with details.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>How do I know if my checklist was reviewed?</strong>
                        <p class="faq-answer answer-yes">Check its status in Report Explorer.<br><strong>Note:</strong> Tier 1 (CROs) will not have access to the "Report Explorer".</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>